io.github.wysohn.gsoncopy.internal.bind

Class JsonTreeReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.wysohn.gsoncopy.stream.JsonReader
      • io.github.wysohn.gsoncopy.internal.bind.JsonTreeReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class JsonTreeReader
extends JsonReader
    This reader walks the elements of a JsonElement as if it was coming from a character stream.
